| Task | Approach | Tokens |
|------|----------|--------|
| Signal listener | Python daemon (zero tokens) | 0 |
| Parse/Enrich/Infer/Risk | Python tools (zero tokens) | 0 |
| Execute trades | MCP calls (zero tokens) | 0 |
| Per-signal decision | Your reasoning | ~200-500 |
| User chat | Full conversation | Variable |
| Error debugging | Source code analysis | Variable |

The heavy lifting (enrichment, inference, risk checks, execution) is all Python — zero LLM tokens. You only spend tokens on reasoning about the model's output and error handling.
